{"tid":988350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基督徒反對《國歌惡法》21/1祈禱會","createTime":"2019-01-20T03:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T09:49:36.000Z","uid":47714,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d484b97c1f0996558af24b2a1371235102ce795d","tid":988350,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://apostlesmedia.com/20190117/11800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2F20190117%2F11800&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=5f61fbc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://apostlesmedia.com/20190117/11800</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://apostlesmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/L.TSANG_.1300.2302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FL.TSANG_.1300.2302.jpg&h=db07724e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《國歌條例草案》(下稱《國歌惡法》)下周三(23日)正式提交立法會審議。「門徒事工」21/1晚在立法會大樓外舉行「基督徒反對《國歌惡法》祈禱會」，祈求《國歌惡法》擱置立法，歡迎所有反對惡法的基督徒參加。<br />\n<br />\n地點：立法會大樓示威區（飯煲底）外<br />\n時間：19:30<br />\n電郵 info@apostlesmedia.com 統計人數<br />\n門徒事工急需事奉人手，進入 <a href=\"http://apostlesmedia.com/joinus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2Fjoinus&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f2d4f0e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://apostlesmedia.com/joinus</a> 登記您可以事奉的崗位"},{"pid":"f405e909e5ce6e122d5fcaff3e9a48099f97ade9","tid":988350,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13aef0a2cdbb9da3aa9d30d2b88b0a38f720dc86","tid":988350,"uid":106426,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9721706f0373e1f98da02e30d98ca93966162373","tid":988350